Name: congenital fibrosis of the extraocular muscles
Definition: An ocular motility disease that is characterized by the inability to move the eyes in certain directions

Name: tolosa-hunt syndrome
Definition: A Kaposi's sarcoma that derives_from the tissue that lines the lymph vessels under the skin or in mucous membranes.

Name: ophthalmoplegia
Definition: A sensory organ benign neoplasm that is located_in the middle ear.
